Gourmet kitchen includes a butler pantry w/wine rack, upgraded cabinets, backsplash, granite countertops, built-in SS kitchen-aid appliances w/6 burner gas cooktop. 6ft master bedroom drop in tub, tiled stand up shower +dual shower heads, separate vanities, his & her closets w/built-ins.
